      "bookmarkId": "3300115119_23_95432-95485",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "95432-95485",
      "markText": "婉刚闭上眼睛，飞机一阵剧烈颠簸。她紧张得全身一缩，仿佛自己的整个人生，也在经历着万米高空之上的剧烈颠簸……",
      "totalCount": 504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115119&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=95432&rangeEnd=95485",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/41d32060813ab9377g019731?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=95432&rangeEnd=95485"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115119_9_18553-18639",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "18553-18639",
      "markText": "对女儿，对女婿，对那做了公公的男人和那做了婆婆的女人，对一个被歪曲了的事实，对他已开始反感的社会本身，教授倒下时决定，该谅解还是要谅解。说完那句话，他的心脏爆裂，就死了……",
      "totalCount": 429,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115119&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=18553&rangeEnd=18639",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/41d32060813ab9377g019731?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=18553&rangeEnd=18639"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115119_10_4917-4968",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "4917-4968",
      "markText": "许多种美的诞生是以另外许多种美的毁灭为代价的，而在这过程中和其后，更会有许多无聊的没意思的事伴随着……",
      "totalCount": 414,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115119&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4917&rangeEnd=4968",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/41d32060813ab9377g019731?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4917&rangeEnd=4968"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115119_5_20637-20706",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "20637-20706",
      "markText": "大柳树村里，周成民那瘦长的身形，伫立在小翠坟头。 月光洒在城乡街，洒在街南街北……",
      "totalCount": 374,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115119&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=20637&rangeEnd=20706",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/41d32060813ab9377g019731?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=20637&rangeEnd=20706"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115119_3_755-837",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "755-837",
      "markText": "如果你当真去找他借钱，向他提出这个要求，他一定会牢记在心，想方设法在第一时间把钱送到你手上。但是钱借出去之后，他便彻底忘了，仿佛这事压根不曾发生，从此再也不会想起。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115119&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=755&rangeEnd=837",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/41d32060813ab9377g019731?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=755&rangeEnd=837"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115119_22_46676-46702",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "46676-46702",
      "markText": "不知是谁草草垒起三个土坟，有一个女人和一个少年行祭。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115119&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=46676&rangeEnd=46702",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/41d32060813ab9377g019731?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=46676&rangeEnd=46702"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115119_5_12677-12717",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "12677-12717",
      "markText": "就在出嫁日子的前三天，小翠喝下了敌敌畏！等家人发现，已经手脚冰凉，死去有些时辰了",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115119&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=12677&rangeEnd=12717",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/41d32060813ab9377g019731?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=12677&rangeEnd=12717"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115119_3_2552-2574",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2552-2574",
      "markText": "记忆不能凭背诵而保有，它只能靠思考获得生命。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115119&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2552&rangeEnd=2574",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/41d32060813ab9377g019731?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2552&rangeEnd=2574"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115119_3_2903-2943",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2903-2943",
      "markText": "最后，我要特别拜托诸位的是，希望你们在看完我的文字之后，千万不要去找梁晓声借钱。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115119&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2903&rangeEnd=2943",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/41d32060813ab9377g019731?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2903&rangeEnd=2943"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115119_20_19089-19128",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "19089-19128",
      "markText": "可是……女哨兵颓然地、僵直地朝后倒了下去，倒在铺雪的大地上，恋恋地瞪视着夜空。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115119&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=19089&rangeEnd=19128",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/41d32060813ab9377g019731?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=19089&rangeEnd=19128"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115119_24_53585-53603",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "53585-53603",
      "markText": "校园里，有更多的孩子们在打闹着了……",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115119&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=53585&rangeEnd=53603",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/41d32060813ab9377g019731?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=53585&rangeEnd=53603"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115119_5_18866-18905",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "18866-18905",
      "markText": "咱俩是哪路的冤家？上辈人们的纠葛与我们有什么相干？要不要你，你后天来听信儿吧！",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300115119&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=18866&rangeEnd=18905",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/41d32060813ab9377g019731?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=18866&rangeEnd=18905"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300115119_18_19842-19908",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "19842-19908",
